Description: Prioritizes candidate disease genes and variants by integrating variant
    pathogenicity (VEP consequence, CADD, splicing via MaxEntScan),
    gene constraint metrics (pLI, pRec, lof_z, mis_z, C1KB), inheritance
    mode (autosomal dominant, autosomal recessive, compound heterozygous,
    X-linked), and phenotypic similarity scores propagated across physical
    and functional gene interaction networks.
